{"type":null,"faqId":17602,"title":"Mate7微信保存的图片无法在图库中显示？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">部分第三方应用，如三联生活周刊，会在文件系统中生成一个隐藏文件夹\".nomedia\"，该文件夹会阻止图库扫描微信等应用保存的图片，请删除这个文件夹，删除方式：<br>\n1、显示文件管理器中的隐藏文件夹，进入应用“文件管理”-右下角“菜单”-设置-勾选“显示隐藏目录和文件”。<br>\n2、删除“.nomedia”文件夹，进入应用“文件管理”-点击“本地”-内部存储-找到“.nomedia”并删除。<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"275","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1419304909000,"seriesProductName":"Jazz-CL00,Jazz-TL00,Jazz-TL10,Jazz-UL00","visitedTimes":960,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Jazz-CL00,Jazz-L09,Jazz-TL00,Jazz-TL10,Jazz-TL20,Jazz-UL00,微信,图片,图库,不显示","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}